name: Saitanobi
description: Saitanobi's main focus is to bring communities together. Wolfpack and Shinjaclan are both incredible crypto communities, welcome Wolfclan to the competition. No longer think of us as just a meme fusion project, Saitanobi Wolfclan is aiming to be the top project in the space attacking the meme market, as well as the utility market. Our first utility which the coin was founded on is buying and supporting Saitama and Shibnobi and rewarding it to our holders through our advanced staking DApp. This is just the beginning of our utilities, we have revolutionary plans to change the space and bring ease and comfortability to investors.
